title: Florida - Themeforest Premium Multipurpose Responsive Theme
description:
Florida is a Responsive, Retina-Ready Wordpress theme with a minimalist, simple, elegant and clean style, a strong focus on contents and readability. It presents a modern business solution. Florida is suitable for multipurpose websites such as business, company, portfolio or blog. It is superbly responsive adapting to any kinds of smart phones and mobile devices. Code is easy to modify and understand so you can personalize it in the easiest way.

To install:
1. Upload the folder to the /wp-content/themes/ directory
2. Activate the theme through the 'Themes' menu in WordPress
